'''Trad Tamaḍalant Tis Snat''' d [[unuɣ]] s yibeckiḍen d rṣaṣ akked wallalen n tmenɣiwt gar tmura n [[umaḍal]] akken ma llant, tebda seg 1 [[ctember]] 1939 ar 2 [[ctember]] 1945. Unuɣ-a yeḍra-d gar snat n tamiwin tigejdanin : [[At tdukli]] d [[Wat tlemmast.|wat tlemmast.<br />]]

Sebba-s d [[Trad Tamaḍalant Tamezwarut]] ur d-yewwin ara tifrat i wuguren akked beqqu n usemɣer n tlisa akked wayen yerzan [[tadamsa]] n tmura n [[wat tlemmast]] ([[Lalman]] [[Tanaẓit]], [[Ṭelyan]] [[Tafacist]] akked Tgelda n [[Japun]]).
